    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>My Cafe Manager Simulator 演示版</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>试用演示版！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 My Cafe Manager Simulator 演示版中，你将从咖啡馆开业的第一天开始，扮演自己的咖啡馆经理。你将学习如何高效地进行客户服务、接单、管理库存和日常运营。了解如何规划菜单、回应客人需求，并保持咖啡馆的顺利运营。这个演示版是掌握关键商业增长策略并创建一个顾客喜欢回来的地方的完美机会！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333170/extras/56cca4a67032b8447f2ff9626626181a.webp?t=1770121182\" width=610 height=49 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333170/extras/09d48d66f94309fa76a8c5650686980c.poster.avif?t=1770121182\" width=610 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333170/extras/09d48d66f94309fa76a8c5650686980c.webm?t=1770121182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333170/extras/09d48d66f94309fa76a8c5650686980c.mp4?t=1770121182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>经营自己的咖啡馆</strong> – 管理库存、装饰和客户服务，打造完美的咖啡馆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333170/extras/d51b48786b324776022d0ad2baafdcc0.webp?t=1770121182\" width=610 height=49 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333170/extras/3f9a2174507b46c5ca3e79a652f7ba6d.poster.avif?t=1770121182\" width=610 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333170/extras/3f9a2174507b46c5ca3e79a652f7ba6d.webm?t=1770121182\" type=